@brl1995 
You sure can. 

Our Minecraft launcher does not touch the Minecraft files, so you can mod it, just like any other Minecraft.

Most mods come with installation instructions but there almost all the same and very easy to follow. Open the Minecraft.jar with file Winrar located in the bin folder, drag the mod files in and delete the metainf folder that is also in the jar. Its really easy.

@Sylevar

With Minecraft there really is no such thing as a cracked server. Minecraft servers have a setting that you can turn off which lets anyone join.

So to answer the question: Anyone can join a cracked server, even people who have bought the game.
